text: Oktyabrevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Allaguvatsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 20 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Sterlibashevo, 5 km from Nizhny Allaguvat. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Oktyabrevka
